{"TopicId":165889,"ForumId":51,"TopicTitle":"Exploring the question, Is there life on the sun?","CreatedByName":"drew4452862","CreatedById":101167,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-26T23:14:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"drew4452862","CreatedById":101167,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-26T23:14:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/4ZHrF\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/4ZHrF\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Richy teh space man","CreatedById":12511,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-26T23:19:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry landing at night and have a look around\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cadet_BNSF","CreatedById":173975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-26T23:22:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223180883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165889\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221506467998\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Richy teh space man\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Richy teh space man said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry landing at night and have a look around\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLOL!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"drew4452862","CreatedById":101167,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-26T23:54:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223180883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165889\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221506467998\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Richy teh space man\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n34 minutes ago, Richy teh space man said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry landing at night and have a look around\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI won\u0027t fall for it.\u00A0 Life needs light to survive\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MrChumley","CreatedById":58555,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-27T00:21:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends on your definition of life I guess. \u00A0According to some schools of thought fire could be considered alive. (Reproduces, consumes...) \u00A0Depending on who you talk to a huge self sustaining ball of fusion reaction might be considered a lifeform in and of itself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ty Tan Tu","CreatedById":167214,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-27T00:46:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223180897\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165889\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221506470094\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022101167\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022drew4452862\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n52 minutes ago, drew4452862 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI won\u0027t fall for it.\u00A0 Life needs light to survive\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are hydrothermal vent creatures in the perpetual night of the deep ocean hydrothermal vents near the Galapagos Rift.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have always wondered about Jupiter. Is it possible, as chemically active as the planet is, that\u00A0there is a layer that could support anaerobic organism? It happens\u00A0on Earth...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-09-27T00:47:23Z\u0022 title=\u002209/27/2017 12:47  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Ty Tan Tu\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-27T00:47:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re playing stock,,,no, it aint gonna\u0027 happen.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aelfhe1m","CreatedById":142910,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-27T02:38:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223180925\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022165889\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221506473203\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167214\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ty Tan Tu\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Ty Tan Tu said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have always wondered about Jupiter. Is it possible, as chemically active as the planet is, that\u00A0there is a layer that could support anaerobic organism? It happens\u00A0on Earth...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell Carl Sagan speculated on the subject (very dated now)\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/KxwkZv4MAGY\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/KxwkZv4MAGY\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1976ApJS...32..737S\u0026amp;amp;data_type=PDF_HIGH\u0026amp;amp;whole_paper=YES\u0026amp;amp;type=PRINTER\u0026amp;amp;filetype=.pdf\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?1976ApJS...32..737S\u0026amp;amp;data_type=PDF_HIGH\u0026amp;amp;whole_paper=YES\u0026amp;amp;type=PRINTER\u0026amp;amp;filetype=.pdf\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a more recent paper speculating on life in the atmospheres of brown dwarfs:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.research.ed.ac.uk/portal/en/publications/atmospheric-habitable-zones-in-y-dwarf-atmospheres(a202e0eb-ebc7-43c8-a0b8-612453e9ee83).html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.research.ed.ac.uk/portal/en/publications/atmospheric-habitable-zones-in-y-dwarf-atmospheres(a202e0eb-ebc7-43c8-a0b8-612453e9ee83).html\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0which cites several other papers about gas giant studies.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-27T15:24:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving to Mission Reports, since the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s post was basically just illustrating a mission he did.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf anyone would like to have actual scientific discussion about the real-life \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003E(no pun intended)\u003C/span\u003E possibility of life on the sun or similar things, feel free to spin up a thread in Science \u0026amp; Spaceflight. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}